reviewText: Fast delivery - great DVD for kids ( adults like it too )
The Octonauts series provides entertainment PLUS learning about sea creatures.  It is both educational and fun for my 4/5 year old grandson.
Grandson loves this dvd.  Watches it frequently.

My girls love the Octonauts. This DVD contains 5 episodes from the Disney Jr. cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. The Enemy Anemones
2. The Remipedes
3. The Hermit Crabs
4. The Humuhumus
5. The Seahorse Tale
My children were happy with this movie.  It was a good value.
